Insider Activity


Individual




Norman H. Wesley



Mr. Norman H. Wesley is on the Board of Directors at Acuity Brands, Inc., Fortune Brands Home & Security, Inc., Acushnet Holdings Corp. and Junior Achievement of Chicago. Mr. Wesley was previously employed as Non-Executive Chairman by Keurig Green Mountain, Inc., an Independent Director by ACCO Brands Corp., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by ACCO World Corp., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by MasterBrand Industries, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Beam, Inc., and Vice President & GM-Office Products Group by Crown Zellerbach Corp. He also served on the board at Pactiv Corp. and R.R. Donnelley & Sons Co. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Utah and an MBA from the University of Utah.



